title: The Sweetea Interview: Blowing Up on Youtube, Pranks, Girls & More
description:
Doknow sits down with Sweetea to talk about their come up, skits, pranks, comedy, building a brand, girls, who's the Beyonce of the group and more!
https://www.instagram.com/doknowsworld_/
https://www.instagram.com/morejuliann/
https://www.instagram.com/frraaannnk/
https://www.instagram.com/kermeq/
https://www.instagram.com/dannyplasce...

-----
00:00 Intro 
0:33 Julian meeting Adam for the first time before they were big
3:45 The no sleep prank and how they flaked on Doknow 
6:25 Banned from Knotts, having their mugshots on the wall at the park 
19:11 Working with Santi when he was growing his fanbase but they noticed him right away
22:06 Who is the most suss of the group?
31:57 Hiding frank under his bed so his mom wouldn't know, she didn't want them to shoot videos
39:38 Latino representation in the media over the last 2/3 years is very promising
43:29 Who's planning on going solo? Who's the Beyonce of the group? 
1:06:09 Doknow has never had his ___ eaten 
1:07:41 They love to ____ in girls' ____
1:08:29 The boys reveal if they would ____ on a girl
1:15:27 The 50 Spiderman prank explained
